# App Router (`src/app`)

- **Prefer RSC**: default to Server Components. Use `'use client'` only at **leaf** interactive components (forms, panels, menus, providers).
- **Examples**: auth forms under `(auth)/`, chat UI [chat-panel.tsx](../../src/app/(app)/chat/chat-panel.tsx), [session-inspector.tsx](../../src/app/(app)/account/session-inspector.tsx), [providers.tsx](../../src/components/providers.tsx).
- **Route groups**: `(marketing)`, `(auth)`, `(app)` — keep new pages in the appropriate group.
- **Proxy** (Next.js 16+): session-gated paths are defined in [proxy.ts](../../src/proxy.ts) (`/dashboard`, `/chat`, `/playground`, `/account`, `/billing`). Add new protected app routes there when needed.
- **API routes** outside `api/auth/*`: follow typed JSON + correct HTTP status; see [api-lib-prisma-auth.mdc](api-lib-prisma-auth.mdc).
